.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, carrot, avocado, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, skydiving, board-games, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, frog, hedgehog
1. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the owner of the cat is the person eating carrot##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
6. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
7. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | avocado   | onion      | carrot       | pear |
| Hobby   | photography | filmmaking | board-games     | skydiving |
| Pet     | hedgehog     | goat  | cat | frog |

