.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, romance, sports, drama
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish, lizard, pony
1. the owner of the lizard is the person watching spy movies##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | sprite          | cola | soy-milk        |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | romance | drama   | spy     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | goldfish         | pony         | lizard |

