.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, skydiving, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, bartender, photographer, dancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, classical, rock, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
2. the photographer is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the dancer is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the fan of classical is between the musician and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
6. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the photographer##3
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | card-games      | skydiving       | traveling    |
| Job           | bartender  | photographer  | dancer | musician |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | rock | classical         | r&b    |

