.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, bartender, dancer, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, hot-chocolate-polo, volleyball
1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the journalist##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the journalist##3
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo##3
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the journalist##1
7. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the software-developer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | mirinda         | almond-milk  | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate         |
| Job        | software-developer | bartender | journalist | dancer         |
| Sport      | handball         | hot-chocolate-polo  | baseball   | volleyball |

