.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, soul, metal, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, polish, thai, german
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, cat, snake
 1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 2. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 4. the thai is between the fan of soul and the fan of rock##2
 5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the owner of the snake is the fan of metal##1
 7. the german is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
 9. the polish is between the fan of blues and the fan of metal##2
10. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | metal    | soul | blues    |
| Nationality   | russian | thai | polish  | german |
| Pet           | cat   | snake    | frog        | goat   |

