.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, electrician, chef, security-guard
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, german, indian, thai
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the electrician is on the left of the photographer##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the chef##3
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the photographer##1
6. the thai is on the right of the electrician##1
7. the german is on the left of the electrician##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the german##3
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | milk                | hot-chocolate  | iced-tea | lemonade   |
| Job           | security-guard | electrician | photographer   | chef |
| Nationality   | german         | argentine     | thai     | indian |

