.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, raspberry, eggplant, pear
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror, fantasy, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, metal, classical, disco
1. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating pear##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the fan of rock is between the person watching adventure movies and the fan of disco##2
6. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant    | raspberry  | pear  | grapefruit |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror | time-travel | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | rock     | disco    | metal |

