.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, water, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, thai, brazilian, japanese
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, bird, rabbit
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person drinking water and the chinese##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the thai##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
7. the chinese is on the left or right of the japanese##3
8. the brazilian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the japanese is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the chinchilla##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | water      | iced-tea  | lemonade    |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | thai | japanese | chinese |
| Pet           | rabbit      | bird       | lizard   | chinchilla      |

