.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, baking, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, mexican, british, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, rugby, badminton
1. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the malaysian##2
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
8. the mexican is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | baking | card-games  | woodworking  |
| Nationality   | british | mexican       | pakistani | malaysian |
| Sport         | rugby   | volleyball      | badminton | baseball       |

