.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, volleyball, skiing, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, van, bus, skateboard
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking water is between the person driving the van and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | water     | 7up    | juice        |
| Sport       | skiing   | lacrosse | volleyball | rugby |
| Transport   | skateboard | bus      | van    | helicopter   |

