The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, trance, techno, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, chinese, pakistani, german
1. the german is in an even position##4
2. the polish is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
3. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of classical##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is the polish##1
6. the fan of techno is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
8. the fan of trance is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster | scientific | thriller   |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | classical   | techno     | soul    |
| Nationality   | chinese  | pakistani | polish  | german |

