.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cucumber, corn, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, skydiving, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, hedgehog, guinea-pig
1. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
5. the person eating cucumber is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | corn    | cucumber    | carrot  | artichoke |
| Hobby   | woodworking | photography | video-games | skydiving      |
| Pet     | frog   | lizard        | guinea-pig   | hedgehog       |

 